BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Pen America": "https://pen.org/event/the-ocean-our-liquid-universe/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:pen_america
SUMMARY:The Ocean: Our Liquid Universe
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260319T193000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260319T193000
UID:da2f8119c25d4498677652dcb7343ca8@pen.org
DESCRIPTION:Cost: 50-300\nDid you know that the Beatles’ “Octopus’s 
 Garden” predated the discovery of four underwater habitats where 6\,000 
 pregnant female octopuses gather in geothermal waters before giving birth?
 \nSet sail with PEN America and WORDTheatre for a one-night-only theatrica
 l event celebrating our blue planet.\nThe Ocean: Our Liquid Universe\n\, w
 hich audiences of all ages into the childlike awe and wonder the sea has i
 nspired for centuries—an exhilarating fusion of music\, stories\, poetry
 \, myth\, and scientific discovery\, brought vividly to life by an all-sta
 r cast of actors\, singers\, and musicians.\nExperience selections from li
 terature such as\nThe Odyssey\nand\nThe Old Man and The Sea\nalongside mus
 ic from Radiohead’s Thom Yorke and The Beatles.\nLearn more\nProfessiona
 l members of PEN America can avail 15% off all non-VIP tickets. If you are
  a member\, please visit the member\nbenefits page\nto access the discount
  code. Not a PEN America member?\nJoin today!
LOCATION:LA
URL:https://pen.org/event/the-ocean-our-liquid-universe/
X-SOURCE:PEN America
END:VEVENT
