DESCRIPTION:This opportunity is open to student newsrooms and journalism s
 chools based in the United States.\nIt’s time to apply if your student n
 ewsroom wants to be part of next year’sStudent Media Challenge– a coho
 rt of student news outlets at colleges and universities that will do solut
 ions reporting on the urgent topic of youth mental health over the 2026-27
  academic year. The Challenge comes with grant money to support reporting 
 and engagement work\, as well as two meetings each month: one with the ent
 ire cohort and me to share progress and benefit from training modules and 
 guest lectures\; and the other with me to troubleshoot and strategize abou
 t your own newsroom’s stories.Apply by March 20.\nJoin us for an info se
 ssion about the program.We're offering two:March 4andMarch 10. Both info s
 essions are at 1 p.m. Eastern Time and advance registration is required.
