UID:57642qjlAH-8228743264@spjnetwork.org
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260320
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260320
SUMMARY:2026 Career Day at the National Press Club
URL:http://www.eventbrite.com/e/2026-career-day-at-the-national-press-club-tickets-1982993687500?aff=oddtdtcreator
DESCRIPTION:Tickets are on sale for Career Day at the National Press Club\, a high-impact event designed for journalists and communicators navigating one of the most challenging job markets our industry has seen in years. 

This year’s programming includes specialized training on staying strategic and motivated after job loss -- plus practical\, hands-on workshops to help you compete in today’s market. Along with visiting news recruiters who are hiring\, you’ll refresh your résumé\, design or elevate your portfolio website\, sharpen your professional pitch\, and connect directly with peers and mentors who can help you get to your next step.

Whether you attend for the full program or drop in for a focused session\, you’ll leave with tangible skills\, actionable next steps\, and something just as important: renewed momentum and community during a time of uncertainty.
LOCATION:National Press Building\, Washington\, DC\, USA
END:VEVENT
