DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260416T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260416T213000
DTSTAMP:20260313T150029
CREATED:20260218T180601Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260218T182113Z
UID:16824-1776364200-1776375000@www.nlgja.org
SUMMARY:Headlines & Headliners
DESCRIPTION:Each year\, this star-studded event raises tens of thousands of dollars for the organization’s programs\, including those that provide scholarships to aspiring LGBTQ+ journalists. Headlines & Headliners draws hundreds of influential journalists\, news executives\, dignitaries and allies to what has become one of New York City’s must-attend media events. \nOnline registration is now open here. \nOnsite registration will be available at the ABC News building\, 7 Hudson Square\, beginning at 6:30 p.m. \n\n\nTICKETS\n$175 for non-members\n$125 for members (Ally\, Associate\, Basic\, International\, LGBTQ\, Retired)\n$50 for Student and Early Career Members\n\n\n\n\n\n\nADDRESS\n7 Hudson Square\n145 Varick Street\nNew York\, NY 10013
URL:https://www.nlgja.org/event/headlines-headliners/
LOCATION:ABC News Building\, 145 Varick Street\, New York\, NY\, United States
CATEGORIES:National
END:VEVENT
