UID:192113c94f69cd7d17b3b192ff526ffd@solutionsjournalism.org
DESCRIPTION:Minneapolis\, Minnesota\, United States\nJoin the Association 
 of Health Care Journalists in Minneapolis for several days of field trips\
 , sessions and networking opportunities. Be sure to mark your calendar for
  the hands-on workshop "Covering Health Disparities From a Solutions Journ
 alism Lens" with Nora Hertel\, executive director of Project Optimist\, an
 d SJN's Wilson Liévano. You'll learn how to recognize leads that can turn
  into solutions stories and how to apply solutions journalism's four pilla
 rs framework. The workshop will be on May 28 from 8:30 a.m. to 10:00 a.m.
LOCATION:Minneapolis\, Minnesota\, United States
URL:https://healthjournalism.org/training-events/health-journalism-2026/
